HEADWORD: Mazdean
<hw>Maz"de*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
<persfn>Ahura-<xex>Mazda</xex></persfn>, or <persfn>Ormuzd</persfn>, the
beneficent deity in the Zoroastrian dualistic system; hence,
Zoroastrian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mazdeism</ent>⟦br⟧
